==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water level
<hw>Wa"ter lev"el</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>The level formed
by the surface of still water.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of leveling instrument. See under
<er>Level</er>, <pos>n.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water lily</ent>⟦br⟧
